projects.name: ArkaEve - Crafting Your Dream Events
projects.description: I developed a comprehensive event management platform using MongoDB, Express.js, Node.js, React, Redux, and RestAPI. The platform provides 60 different themes and over 20 vendor options to optimize the operations of large-scale event organizers. Created an Administrative dashboard for System Administrators to oversee Dealers, Event Planners, Transactions and other Backend tasks improving overall platform efficiency and management.

projects.name: Twooter
projects.description: It is a social media platform used to upload your daily life updates. It allows you to post, comment, and create an account. It has the ability to save your posts and search your account. The Front End is built with ReactJS, CSS, and HTML to showcase all the features. Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB power the backend to handle data storage, updates, and APIs. It also uses dummy JSON to fetch sample data from the website.

projects.name: SideCup Family Golf
projects.description: Dive into the captivating world of Sidecup Family Show with this immersive web experience! This project is a showcase of my skills in web development, bringing to life a modern and engaging interface inspired by the essence of Sidecups familyfriendly content. Technologies Utilized: HTML, CSS, JavaScript. Key Features: Visually stunning design for an enchanting user experience. Dynamic elements powered by HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
